                     <interp inst="t17700912-54-person460" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was at the Red-Lion. There was nobody near the tankard but the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I never was in the house in my life.</p>
